{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/14-last-stone-weight/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c49b8366-0c94-579a-8b12-dbed951952a8","excerpt":"벌써 Day13 이다!!😳 오늘 문제는 easy 문제이고, 나는 바로 풀진 못했지만 우선순위 큐를 이용하면 금방 해결할 수 있는 문제였다.  문제 요약 input으로 array가 들어온다. 그중에서 큰 숫자 2개를 선택하고 그 두 숫자가 다를 경우에 숫자를 부순다! \n부순다는 것은 그 두 수는 없애고 두 수의 차를 array…","html":"<p>벌써 Day13 이다!!😳 오늘 <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/last-stone-weight/\">문제</a>는 easy 문제이고, 나는 바로 풀진 못했지만 우선순위 큐를 이용하면 금방 해결할 수 있는 문제였다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 79.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"last-stone-weight\"\n        title=\"last-stone-weight\"\n        src=\"/static/dab65d3f66d5475847065cd141babf65/e5166/last-stone-weight.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dab65d3f66d5475847065cd141babf65/f93b5/last-stone-weight.jpg 300w,\n/static/dab65d3f66d5475847065cd141babf65/b4294/last-stone-weight.jpg 600w,\n/static/dab65d3f66d5475847065cd141babf65/e5166/last-stone-weight.jpg 1200w,\n/static/dab65d3f66d5475847065cd141babf65/b79f3/last-stone-weight.jpg 1244w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>input으로 array가 들어온다. 그중에서 큰 숫자 2개를 선택하고 그 두 숫자가 다를 경우에 숫자를 부순다!\n부순다는 것은 그 두 수는 없애고 두 수의 차를 array에 추가하는 방식이다. 이렇게 반복을 해서 선택된 두 수가 같을때까지 반복한다.\n최종적으로 부숴진 수를 리턴하는 것이 문제다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>먼저 내림차순 정렬을 하고, 첫번째와 두번째 값을 비교해서 부수는 과정을 진행한다. 그리고 부순 숫자를 배열에 넣고 다시한번 정렬. 이 과정을 반복한다.\n언제까지 반복하냐면? 배열의 크기가 1보다 클 때까지 반복한다.\n그러다가 배열의 크기가 0이면 0을 리턴하고 1개일 경우에는 하나 남은 항목 <code class=\"language-text\">stones[0]</code>을 리턴해준다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-priority-queue\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-priority-queue\" aria-label=\"1 priority queue permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) Priority Queue</h2>\n<p>이 문제가 왜 우선순위 큐 문제냐면,\n큐는 보통 FIFO을 따르지만 우선순위큐는 들어간 순서에 상관없이 우선순위가 높은 데이터가 먼저 나오기 떄문이다. (sorting을 통해)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>시간 복잡도: O(N)</li>\n<li>공간 복잡도: O(1)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>문제집 솔루션은 락이 잠겨있어서 확인하지 못했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {number[]} stones\n * @return {number}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">lastStoneWeight</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">stones</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> s1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> s2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">unshift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">abs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s1 <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> s2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> stones<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"소감\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%90\" aria-label=\"소감 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>소감</h2>\n<p>쉬운 문제여서 풀 수 있었을 것 같은데 알고리즘 한 지 몇일 됬다고 벌써 권태기가 왔다;;;</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"🌩Last Stone Weight","date":"April 13, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/dab65d3f66d5475847065cd141babf65/14b42/last-stone-weight.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/14-last-stone-weight/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/xss-and-content-security-policy/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"XSS and Content Security Policy","category":"javascript","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/15-perform-string-shifts/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"👣 Perform String Shifts","category":"algorithm","draft":false}}}}}